@node Overview
@chapter Overview

@samp{ace-link-extras.el} extends @samp{ace-link}, the package that uses @samp{avy} to let you jump to and open visible links with a few keystrokes. While @samp{ace-link} provides mode-specific commands for common contexts (Org, EWW, Info, etc.), it does not handle all the ways links may appear---for example, HTML emails rendered by @samp{w3m}, or the backlink sidebar of @samp{org-roam}.

This package adds commands for four contexts:

@itemize
@item
Opening links in @samp{mu4e} message buffers, with special handling for the @samp{w3m} HTML renderer (@ref{mu4e link opening}).
@item
Opening EWW links in an external browser or a new buffer (@ref{EWW link actions}).
@item
Following links in @samp{org-roam-mode} backlink buffers (@ref{Org-roam link following}).
@end itemize

