@node Link extraction
@section Link extraction

@findex ace-link-extras-w3m-get-url
The function @code{ace-link-extras-w3m-get-url} extracts a URL from a @samp{w3m}-rendered buffer. It uses @samp{avy} to let you select a link from those collected by @code{ace-link--w3m-collect}, then returns the URL string from the @samp{w3m-href-anchor} text property at the selected position. This function is called internally by @code{ace-link-extras-mu4e} (@ref{mu4e link opening}).

